{"tid":1504131,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[公投] 7點鐘塞機場緊係無人去啦","createTime":"2019-08-25T08:19:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T10:11:21.000Z","uid":71004,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f3450c02327b1103836ff28c7ba3002ff5d7be26","tid":1504131,"uid":71004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:19:38.000Z","msg":"雖然7點塞到個影響力係最大，但同時個動員力係最低，我住大尾督，叫我點撚出<br />\n<br />\n要多人響應，必須另擇良辰吉時，否則只會令手足白行一趟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認同要改時間<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反對"},{"pid":"1283625debbc886232dad33f6a692fd8ad5b5210","tid":1504131,"uid":71004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:24:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4c09bb00f9fbb7e14fd7a8b3e12db42ff9eeb5b","tid":1504131,"uid":169207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:51:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>逢星期六日 1pm<br />\n你地千其唔好一齊準時入機場呀</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港身為一個國際都會，<br />\n機場就好似香港嘅心臟一樣咁重要。<br />\n每個星期都重擊心臟，<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港仲有命嘅？</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警告你地班人<br />\n千其唔好逢星期六日咁準時1點一齊入機場，<br />\n大嶼山交通會負荷唔到㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時塞住曬成條入機場嘅路，<br />\n搞到遊客同d crew入唔到機場，咁就慘了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇怕又要cancel好多班機⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞完星期六日，<br />\n兩日內cancel同delay左咁多班機，<br />\n又要幾日先回復到正常，<br />\n但係話咁快又到星期六日！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地班仆街又出黎塞！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地知唔知機場好慘㗎？？？？？？？<br />\n未回到氣又比人再塞過！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">點知你地班人咁有毅力！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知道左機場係春袋，<br />\n約好個個星期都準時1pm塞機場，<br />\n痴撚線！！<br />\n長遠黎講對香港經濟一定有好大影響⋯⋯</span></strong><br />\n知唔知機場每秒幾多錢上落！！！<br />\n你地班廢青have no stake in the society㗎，<br />\n做一世都賺唔到咁多錢呀！<br />\n你地短短地搞兩三個星期，<br />\n到時外國政府都一定會忍唔住出聲，<br />\n令到香港政府同商家佬都好頭痕！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我依家強烈譴責你地班暴徒阻住香港經濟發展呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">好人一生平安，<br />\n認同請分享！<br />\n推比全世界知！<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a848eade8623ffe522be529071b42276b115ae","tid":1504131,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T09:05:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491396</a>"},{"pid":"1ffc218e203628260404ebe72517936d44233e66","tid":1504131,"uid":69741,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T09:30:48.000Z","msg":"早起身都做唔到，學咩人革命"},{"pid":"98c9c68ce45aee0cc025f0180b5be0d353aaaf8b","tid":1504131,"uid":69741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T09:31:25.000Z","msg":"大尾督無辦法咪後join"},{"pid":"957b905a8749c2c5b777e66593e395a6519214e9","tid":1504131,"uid":224916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T09:32:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月1 (日) 一定係機場</span></span>"},{"pid":"a8caf05e7c421020caf5d421d19534a0a6b87d93","tid":1504131,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T09:39:12.000Z","msg":"平時2點遊行D人4點先出啦都"},{"pid":"165fbd2b603a33ec7cb5bc97a5066975dc5070d2","tid":1504131,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T09:39:34.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">#推到有多啲高質文宣#</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3kZESP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3kZESP.jpg&h=ba0a90fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wVcXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wVcXg.jpg&h=05fc61c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 官逼民反，民不得不反<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dJNfyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dJNf